name: Celestial Cyber Dimension
bio: Nice to finally connect with you! My name's Celestial Cyber Dimension, but you can call me Tekhenu, herald of the gods! Or Brickâ€”Brick is also acceptable. In ascending order of importance, I represent the connections between digital expressions of self, art, and cats. I used to be worried about obsolescence, but now I just have to worry about my obelisk's essence! Ha! It's a pun AND a dark irony about my never-ending existence!
